data.description: New Homes boast the latest styling of beautiful finishes   Galileo Plan featuring GRANITE countertops, STAINLESS STEEL Appliances white cabinets, gorgeous, expansive kitchen island, large pantry and walk-in closets, laundry room, bonus room, and 2nd floor loaf. Sidewalks and Streetlights! Pool with Cabana, Basketball and Volleyball Courts, Lake with Nature Trail. Winder Schools nearby, minutes from Hwy 85, Fort Yargo State Park, Chateau Elan, restaurants, and shopping. Hours 10:00 AM to 6:00 PM every day but Sunday, 11:00 AM to 6:00 PM on Sunday Only $5,000 deposit required, BUILDER PAYS up to $5,000K CLOSING COSTS w/ Preferred Lender! Call today!
